snippet.title: Prehistoric Hunt - Dinosaur Trailer
snippet.description:
Available now on Steam Early Access! Get it now and jump in a dinosaur hunting adventure with your friends! https://store.steampowered.com/app/752900/Prehistoric_Hunt/
Join the community on our Discord: https://discord.gg/a6GVj32

Prehistoric Hunt is a daring hunting adventure where the land is filled with dangerous dinosaurs. Be smarter than your opponent and score your biggest catches.
